parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt retractor sticks or fails
the seat belt does not retract
the seat belt does not work properly
the retractor does not work all the time
the seat belt exhibits false latching.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine fires can cause significant damage to the vehicle, potentially leading to costly repairs or even total loss. In extreme cases, engine fires can spread to other parts of the vehicle, posing a risk to the occupants and bystanders.

oil shooting out of the dipstick

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty intake gasket can cause engine failure, leading to a loss of power and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
Engine failure can cause a loss of power, potentially leaving the driver stranded and increasing the risk of accidents.
